<h1>@HI{{mama}}</h1>

<h2> Formation </h2>

<p>
<ol>
<li> @Vplain{{}}(past) <strong>@HI{{mama}}</strong>
<li> @Ai{{}} <strong>@HI{{mama}}</strong>
<li> @Ana{{}} <strong>@HI{{mama}}</strong>
<li> @N{{}} @HI{{no }}<strong>@HI{{mama}}</strong>
</ol>
</p>

<h2> Definition </h2>

<strong>@HI{{mama}}</strong> indicates that a situation remains unaltered.
<p></p>

<h2> Examples </h2>

<ol>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
    @HI{{@KJ{{younger*brother}}ha @KT{{terebi}}wo tsuketa <strong>mama</strong> @KJ{{lie*down}}te shimaimashita.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
    My younger brother went to sleep leaving the TV on.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
    @HI{{@KJ{{younger*brother}}ha @KT{{terebi}}wo tsuketa <strong>mama</strong> ni shite okimashita.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
    My younger brother left the TV on.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
    @HI{{@KJ{{younger*brother}}ha @KT{{terebi}}wo tsuketa <strong>mama</strong> desu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
    My younger brother has left the TV on.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
    @HI{{kono @KJ{{section^roof}}ha kinou no <strong>mama</strong> desu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
    This room is as it was yesterday.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence" border=0>
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
    @HI{{@KJ{{cap^child}} kabutta <strong>mama</strong> no @KJ{{study^life}}ga @KJ{{teach^room}}ni imashita.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
    There was a student still wearing a hat in the classroom.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</ol>

